# Notes Folder

This folder contains ideas, research, and reference material.

## How to Use

Store your raw material here:
- Content ideas
- Research notes
- Voice memo transcripts
- Inspiration and references
- Meeting notes
- Interview transcripts

Claude can draw from these when creating content.

## Organization Tips

Create subfolders as needed:
- /ideas - Raw content ideas
- /research - Topic research
- /transcripts - Voice memos and interviews
- /references - Inspiration from others
- /templates - Your own templates
